Cell.Text: S|I wasn't expecting to see you here! I assume you have your reasons. Everyone does.
Look around the room and you'll see what we're up against. Just between you and me, a lot of what Ulfric says about the Empire is true.
I swear Elenwen holds these parties just to make the Empire look bad. Almost makes me want to join the Stormcloaks.
The only reason I'm here is because my refusal to attend would cause a diplomatic incident.
I don't remember seeing you at one of these before.
Do I know you? I didn't think so.
That's putting it mildly. | The Thalmor invite me here to remind everyone that they can tell the Empire what to do. | I would refuse, but I don't want to jeopardize the peace between us.

Node.Caption: MQ201PartyTulliusAwkwardTopic: This must be awkward for you.

Cell.Text: Elenwen is a formidable woman. She lacks for neither cunning nor ambition. | Now that I think of it, she would have made a fine Imperial general.
